item.title: About
item.dc:creator: TKDEMOS
item.content:encoded:
Hi! My name is Charlotte Johnson, and I’m a fashion blogger. If you are a bit of a fashionista, you are in the right place.

Here’s everything you need to know about me.

I grew up in San Francisco. At a very young age, I noticed that my mother was obsessed with makeup and fashion. She had dozens of dresses and hundreds of shoes, and I loved going through all of them and playing dress-up. My childhood was colored with the smell of high-end purses, clutches, dresses, overalls, and makeup.

Although I was the ultimate girly girl, I must say I was a bit of a bookworm. My biggest dream was to study Fashion Design. I went to the Academy of Art’s School, and the dream came true. After I got my Bachelor’s degree, I started working as an Assistant Manager at Tonlé. I was more than happy working there, but I’ve always felt like I wanted to achieve more.
